 - **原因**: context canceled\n  - **证据**: `\"failed to get product recommendations: rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled\"`\n\n### 错误信息输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"context canceled\", \"Connection timed out\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Connection timed out\",\n      \"evidence\": \"debug_error_string = \\\"Error received from peer ... Connection timed out\\\"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"context canceled\",\n      \"evidence\": \"\\\"failed to get product recommendations: rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled\\\"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n基于以上分析，请考虑检查推荐服务的网络连接和响应时间，以解决 `frontend` 服务遇到的请求取消问题。", "trace_analysis_findings": "### 数据分析结果\n\n#### 关键异常发现\n\n1. **延迟异常**:\n   - `RecommendationService/ListRecommendations` 被多次调用，延迟显著增加。和正常平均耗时相比，异常时段平均耗时增加了近 **4770 倍**（如 `frontend-0 到 frontend-0`, `frontend-2 到 frontend-2`)。\n   - `ProductCatalogService/GetProduct` 在 `frontend-0 到 productcatalogservice-0` 的调用也有显著延迟，约为正常时段的 **1.5 倍**。\n   - `CurrencyService/GetSupportedCurrencies` 出现延迟翻倍的现象，约 **1.7 倍**。\n\n2. **错误传播**:\n   - `RecommendationService/ListRecommendations` 在多个前端实例中显示 `context canceled` 错误，说明此调用可能牵连到了全局异常。\n   - `RecommendationService/ListRecommendations` 还显示出多个 `Connection timed out` 错误，强调了与 `recommendationservice` 相关的问题。\n\n3. **主要瓶颈节点**:\n   - **RecommendationService** 在多个前端节点上同时表现异常，延迟剧增可能与 `recommendationservice-2` 相关。\n   - 网络请求频繁超时，特别是涉及 `RecommendationService` 的调用。\n\n#### 可能的异常根因\n\n- **Recommendation Service** 的 `recommendationservice-2` 实例可能为主要问题源，导致大量超时和 `context canceled` 状态。\n- 延迟的显著增加和错误状态集中在 `RecommendationService` 请求中，可能是因为该服务在异常期间承受的负载过大导致处理能力下降。\n\n### 输出指标和假设\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"frontend->recommendationservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"RecommendationService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"异常平均响应时间超过正常的4770倍，且伴随严重超时错误\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ProductCatalogService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"响应时间为正常的1.5倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CurrencyService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"响应时间为正常的1.7倍\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n需要进一步调查 `recommendationservice` 的具体实例健康状态、负载情况以及任何网络通信异常。此外，需关注上下游服务的健康性以确定是否尽速恢复正常。", "metric_analysis_findings": "### 分析报告\n\n#### 异常指标\n\n从数据中提取的显著变化指标为：\n\n- `client_error_ratio`\n- `error_ratio`\n- `server_error_ratio`\n- `rrt`\n- `rrt_max`\n- `pod_cpu_usage`\n\n#### 检测到的异常调用链\n\n以下是异常指标所影响的具体组件和相关变化：\n\n1. **Component: Shipping Service Pods**\n   - **shippingservice-0**, **shippingservice-1**, **shippingservice-2**\n   - **Reason**: `client_error_ratio`, `error_ratio` 指标均显著异常，故障期间中位数从 0 上升到 60。\n   - **Evidence**: 高达200%变化率。\n   \n2. **Component: Frontend Service Pods**\n   - **frontend-0**, **frontend-1**, **frontend-2**\n   - **Reason**: `server_error_ratio`, `rrt`, `rrt_max` 显著上升。`server_error_ratio`故障期间中位数从 0 上升到 15.79。\n   - **Evidence**: 整体服务响应时间激增，后台请求延迟急剧上升。\n   \n3. **Component: Recommendation Service Pods**\n   - **recommendationservice-2**\n   - **Reason**: `rrt_max`异常高，中位数从正常的 13148.0 上升到 0.0。\n   - **Evidence**: 请求最大响应时间高达 21,369.2，存在明显的性能问题。\n   \n4. **Component: Redis Cart Pod**\n   - **redis-cart-0**\n   - **Reason**: `pod_cpu_usage` 在故障期间发生无故变化。\n   - **Evidence**: CPU 使用特征发生非正常波动，可能影响系统稳定性。\n\n这些异常指标提示系统可能存在严重的服务性能和资源使用不一致的问题。需要进一步调查特定服务和 Pod 的日志和使用情况，以准确定位根因。\n\n### 输出 JSON 格式\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"server_error_ratio\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"shippingservice Pods experienced abnormal client_error_ratio and error_ratio indicating potential request handling issues.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Both metrics' median changed from 0 to 60 with a change ratio of 2.0.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Frontend service exhibited high server_error_ratio and excessive latency in rrt and rrt_max, indicating backend processing delays.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Server error ratio increased to 15.79, rrt max increased to 60001776.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"Recommendation service rrt_max indicated unresponsiveness or high processing time.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Maximum response time decreased to 0 in median but high spikes recorded in fault p99.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod CPU sporadic usage indicating resource contention or transient application issues.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Pod CPU usage showed unexpected spikes.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n此解决方案依赖于提供的指标进行初步分析，建议在实际操作中进一步验证并细化调整。"}
